ize: 13px; padding: 9.5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.42857; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-radius: 4px; font-family: &#39;Courier New&#39; !important; background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);\">$_mysqli-&gt;query(&quot;CREATE&nbsp;DATABASE&nbsp;IF&nbsp;NOT&nbsp;EXISTS&nbsp;数据库名&nbsp;DEFAULT&nbsp;CHARACTER&nbsp;SET&nbsp;utf8&nbsp;COLLATE&nbsp;utf8_general_ci;&quot;);$_mysqli-&gt;query(&quot;USE&nbsp;数据库名&quot;);</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; color: rgb(94, 94, 94); font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 10px auto; white-space: normal; color: rgb(94, 94, 94); font-family: Verdana, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</span>将数据库名换成你需要修改的名称即可！更多的功能大家可自行探索！</p><p><br/></p>','利用PHP执行SQL文件，将SQL文件导入到数据库','如何利用php自动执行.sql文件。其实很简单，就是获取sql文件中的内容，然后将每一句sql语句一次执行就行啦。','1','1','2016-07-29 09:58:01','','0','','','0','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','1','0','0','0');
INSERT INTO cmf_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended` ) VALUES  ('17','1','','','2016-07-29 10:02:29','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">使用PHP开发应用程序，尤其是网站程序，常常需要生成随机密码，如用户注册生成随机密码，用户重置密码也需要生成一个随机的密码。随机密码也就是一串固定长度的字符串，这里我收集整理了几种生成随机字符串的方法，以供大家参考。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">方法一：</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1、在 33 – 126 中生成一个随机整数，如 35，</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2、将 35 转换成对应的ASCII码字符，如 35 对应 #</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3、重复以上 1、2 步骤 n 次，连接成 n 位的密码</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">该算法主要用到了两个函数，mt_rand ( int $min , int $max )函数用于生成随机整数，其中 $min – $max 为 ASCII 码的范围，这里取 33 -126 ，可以根据需要调整范围，如ASCII码表中 97 – 122 位对应 a – z 的英文字母，具体可参考 ASCII码表； chr ( int $ascii )函数用于将对应整数 $ascii 转换成对应的字符。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">function create_password($pw_length = 8)</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">{</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">$randpwd = &#39;&#39;;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">for ($i = 0; $i &lt; $pw_length; $i++)</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">{</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">$randpwd .= chr(mt_rand(33, 126));</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">}</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">return $randpwd;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">}</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">// 调用该函数，传递长度参数$pw_length = 6</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">echo create_password(6);</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700;\">方法二：</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1、预置一个的字符串 $chars ，包括 a – z，A – Z，0 – 9，以及一些特殊字符</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2、在 $chars 字符串中随机取一个字符</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3、重复第二步 n 次，可得长度为 n 的密码</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">function generate_password( $length = 8 ) {</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">// 密码字符集，可任意添加你需要的字符</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">$chars = &#39;abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyzABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ0123456789!@#$%^&amp;*()-_ []{}&lt;&gt;~`+=,.;:/?|&#39;;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">$password = &#39;&#39;;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">for ( $i = 0; $i &lt; $length; $i++ )</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">{</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">// 这里提供两种字符获取方式</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">// 第一种是使用 substr 截取$chars中的任意一位字符；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">// 第二种是取字符数组 $chars 的任意元素</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">// $password .= substr($chars, mt_rand(0, strlen($chars) - 1), 1);</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">$password .= $chars[ mt_rand(0, strlen($chars) - 1) ];</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">}</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">return $password;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">}</p><p><br/></p>','php生成随机密码的几种方法','使用PHP开发应用程序，尤其是网站程序，常常需要生成随机密码，如用户注册生成随机密码，用户重置密码也需要生成一个随机的密码。随机密码也就是一串固定长度的字符串，这里我收集整理了几种生成随机字符串的方法，以供大家参考。','1','1','2016-07-29 09:59:11','','0','','','1','{\"thumb\":\"\"}','2','1','0','0');
INSERT INTO cmf_posts ( `id`, `post_author`, `post_keywords`, `post_source`, `post_date`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `post_modified`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`, `smeta`, `post_hits`, `post_like`, `istop`, `recommended` ) VALUES  ('22','1','','','2016-07-29 10:28:24','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">SSH（Secure Shell）是一种通用的、功能强大的、基于软件的网络安全解决方案。计算机每次向网络发送数据时，SSH都会自动对其进行加密。数据到达目的地时，SSH自动对加密数据进行解密。整个过程都是透明的，使用OpenSSH工具将会增进你的系统安全性。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　谈到网络安全访问，相信大家首先想到的就是安全Shell，也就是Secure Shell，通常简写为SSH。这是因为SSH安装容易、使用简单，而且比较常见，一般的Unix系统、Linux系统、FreeBSD系统都附带有支持SSH的应用程序包。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><img src=\"http://test.sixth.cn/data/upload