rosoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 35px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-edit\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; top: 1px; display: inline-block; font-family: &#39;Glyphicons Halflings&#39;; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"></span>&nbsp;使用方法</h3><h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-paperclip\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; top: 1px; display: inline-block; font-family: &#39;Glyphicons Halflings&#39;; line-height: 1; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\"></span>&nbsp;HTML结构</h5><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px 13px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">该幻灯片特效的HTML结构包含3个无序列表：一个是<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 14.4px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">ul.gallery</code>，一个<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 14.4px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">ul.navigation</code>是前后导航缩略图，<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 14.4px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">ul.caption</code>是各个图片的描述信息。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 4px 0px 13px; border: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Tahoma, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 30px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 14.4px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">ul.gallery</code>中的每一个列表项由一个<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 14.4px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">.svg-wrapper</code>元素来包裹一个<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 14.4px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">&lt;svg&gt;</code>元素。在<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 14.4px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">&lt;svg&gt;</code>元素中又包含一个<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 14.4px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">&lt;clipPath&gt;</code>元素，它用于改变图片的剪裁区域。还有一个<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &#39;Courier New&#39;, monospace; font-size: 14.4px; padding: 2px 4px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244);\">&lt;image